</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-58_ pf-text-1"><strong>Practical training</strong> - Effective CPR training should include practical sessions to practice techniques on mannequins, allowing participants to learn the physical aspect of delivering CPR.

